text: Except as disclosed in, “Management’s Discussion and Analysis of Financial Condition and Results of Operations – Significant Developments After June 30, 2025, That May Affect Our Future Results Of Operations” on page 386, there have not arisen, since the date of the last financial information disclosed in this Draft Red Herring Prospectus, any circumstances which materially and adversely affect, or are likely to affect, our operations, our profitability taken as a whole or the value of our consolidated assets or our ability to pay our liabilities within the next 12 months.
